overview.en: DeepToken’s mission is to discover quality AI projects.We believe that the core of an exchange is to discover quality digital asset and, in terms bring return on users’ investments. DeepToken propose the innovative ‘’Voting Mining’’ mechanism, AI experts and practitioners will screen projects to find outstanding digital assets from the AI industry.
overview.zh: DeepToken使命：发掘人工智能行业的优质币我们认为交易所的核心价值在于找到优质的数字资产，从而让交易所的用户受益。DeepToken推出创新性的投票即挖矿模式，通过人工智能专家及从业者的筛选，从而找到人工智能领域优质的数字资产。注：此为 DPT 官方发行的旧 DPT 代币。新 DPT 合约地址：0x4eD413557F4248cb1aD0eAf1469e164aD820391d
